frames.caption: Two cats sit on a rooftop, gazing at the moonlit cityscape. A glass of red wine and a plate of food are placed between them, creating a serene and intimate setting. The city lights twinkle in the distance, with a prominent tower glowing brightly.
frames.description: The scene depicts a tranquil night on a city rooftop, where two cats are enjoying the view of a bustling city under the moonlight. The atmosphere is calm and peaceful, with the city skyline and a prominent tower in the background.
